          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To make agents ("
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/gameplaykit/gkagent"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " objects) avoid obstacles, create a goal with the "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": true,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/gameplaykit/gkgoal/1501098-goaltoavoidobstacles"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " method. Agents affected by an avoid-obstacles goal will attempt to move such that their radius never overlaps that of a spherical obstacle."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To learn more about using goals and agents, see "
            },
